Interface IBusMirrorChannelMappingCan

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IBusMirrorChannelMapping, IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable

    public interface IBusMirrorChannelMappingCan
extends IEntity, IBusMirrorChannelMapping
    IBusMirrorChannelMappingCan: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This element defines the bus mirroring between a CAN or LIN sourceChannel and a CAN targetChannel.
